  "claimBoundary": "V11 proves that one clipped GRPO-with-KL update from 96 nonzero-advantage samples improved one seed-11 Qwen 3.5 9B SFT policy on 299 family-disjoint public WGSL compiler-repair tasks under one frozen sampler and Radeon verifier runtime. It does not prove multi-seed stability, semantic ML-kernel correctness, causal benefit from external SFT curation, or promotion. The matched 400-step DPO lane is rejected.",
